  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced, wave based zombie shooter game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >the current features include:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22 weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 equipment items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon customization (skins/colours)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ability to import custom weapon skins (only available for some guns)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dual wielding</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 main maps + 2 seasonal maps + 3 extra maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 normal enemy types + 1 seasonal one</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online leaderboard</p></li></ul>",
